<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">身加减满法，是指互为补数的两数相减，将大数身加（即原数加原数），再减其满数的一种求差方法。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">68-32=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">68-32</Run>
    </Paragraph>
     <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=68+68-100</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=136-100</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>